metadata.name: Lillibeth WKND #01
metadata.description: WEEKs are valid from Monday to Friday and WKNDs from Friday to Sunday. So, whenever you feel like staying in the SKS Castle, get yourself either the WEEK or WKND NFT and start packing your suitcase. Your NFTS are valid for 20 years, throughout the year. As we want to prepare everything according to your needs, we would kindly ask you to announce your arrival two weeks in advance. Once arrived, your NFT is burned, and you can enjoy your luxurious stay in our outstanding castle.
